						<summary>

						<p>Hero-stone lying near the house of Jivvimānu Pochi-Reḍḍi.</p>						

						<p>Mutilated. It mentions a certain Muttarāju, probably the hero depicted on the stone and refers to a fight. In characters of 8th century A.D.</p>						

